const HardDrives = forwardRef<SVGSVGElement, IconProps>((props, ref) => {

    color: contextColor,
    size: contextSize,
    weight: contextWeight,
    mirrored: contextMirrored,

  return (
    <svg

      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width={size ?? contextSize}
